OL,3,CMan who stabbed pregnant woman in
OL,4,CAberfan admits attempted murder
OL,6,FA 29-year-old man has admitted the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of a pregnant woman
OL,8,Fin Aberfan.
OL,10,FDaniel Popescu, of no fixed abode,
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to attempted murder
OL,12,Ffollowing the attack in Aberfan,
OL,13,FMerthyr Tydfil, on December 5, 2023.
OL,15,FThe village of Aberfan was brought to
OL,16,Fa standstill due to the incident, with
OL,17,Femergency services called to the scene
OL,18,Faround 9.10am and schools going into
OL,19,Flockdown as armed police searched for
OL,20,Fthe knifeman.
