OL,6,FThe woman suffered at least five stab
OL,7,Fwounds during the assault, and was
OL,8,Funder police guard while receiving
OL,9,Ftreatment in hospital. She was
OL,10,Fdischarged in the days after the
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FPopescu appeared in Cardiff Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Thursday, 4 April, where he
OL,15,Falso admitted a stalking offence.
