OL,3,CMan who stabbed pregnant woman in
OL,4,CAberfan admits attempted murder
OL,6,FThe court heard that between October
OL,7,F25, 2023, and December 6, 2023, the
OL,8,Fdefendant followed the woman, called
OL,9,Fher from withheld numbers, filmed her
OL,10,Fand placed the footage on TikTok, and
OL,11,Fsat outside her home.
OL,13,FThe defendant denied a further charge
OL,14,Fof intimidation of a witness.
OL,15,FProsecutor John Hipkins KC said he did
OL,16,Fnot wish to proceed with a trial in
OL,17,Frespect of this count, which he asked
OL,18,Fto lie on file.
